id: pm-srex
title: "Audit (2026-06-07): CLI surface & schema/config"
description: "Systematic read-only audit of CLI command surface, agent ergonomics, schema/config subsystem, and contract coverage. Scope: src/cli/, src/sdk/cli-contracts.ts, src/core/config/, src/core/schema/, src/core/store/settings-validator.ts, governance logic, docs/COMMANDS.md, docs/CONFIGURATION.md, docs/AGENT_GUIDE.md. Methodology: rg/grep/Read code, run pm --help/contracts/schema, cross-reference existing children of pm-mpbb and pm-8jdc, file OPEN forward backlog items only."
type: Story
status: open
priority: 2
tags[3]: "area:cli","area:schema",audit
